Use the standard library
This is how to modp of n and p:
  When p is 0, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  Remember that result is 1
  Remember that base is remainder of n and p
  Remember that exp is p
  Do this p times:
    When exp is 0, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    When remainder of exp and 2 is 1, then:
      Remember that result is remainder of product of result and base and p
    End when
    Remember that base is remainder of product of base and base and p
    Remember that exp is quotient of exp and 2
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know